description: Ameriwood Home Farmington Wide Storage Cabinet, 31.5", Rustic GrayThe System Build Farmington 31.5” Wide Storage Cabinet is a stylish way to stay on top of your organization. The rustic barn style design and sleek tapered feet gives the look of an old weathered cabinet but the sturdy laminated particleboard and MDF make this cabinet the perfect piece to house your home office supplies, extra linens, seasonal clothing, nonperishable food and more! Open up the two doors to 4 spacious shelves, 2 adjustable, to fit items of differing sizes. The weathered brown finish with gray undertones will bring a nice rustic appeal to your space. The Farmington Cabinet is recommended to be assembled and moved by 2 adults. A wall anchor kit is provided for extra safety and security.
